Daniella Monet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniella_Monet 0 Daniella Monet Zuvic (born March 1, 1989) is an American actress and singer best known for playing numerous television guest roles and starring as Trina Vega in the Nickelodeon comedy series Victorious. She also played Rebecca in the Nickelodeon comedy-drama series Zoey 101 and the supporting role of Inga Veinshtein in the 2007 film Nancy Drew.
